{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896067235,"sessionID":"ses_2845c53fbffePPAJ9umtY57fu2","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba3b867001BiKgPWosLeXlof","messageID":"msg_d7ba3acff001LmrA6M3QEwJIiB","sessionID":"ses_2845c53fbffePPAJ9umtY57fu2","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_b3b5c283ba85446bb14201df","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure - what directories exist at the root and key subdirectories\n2. The test/e2e directory - what exists there currently, any existing e2e test patterns\n3. Any existing test patterns (unit tests, integration tests) to understand conventions\n4. The main application components that would need e2e testing - look at cmd/, internal/, pkg/ directories\n5. Any existing design documents, specs, or stage documentation (look for ST-3, design docs, plans.md, tasks.md files)\n6. Any configuration files (go.mod, Makefile, etc.) that show dependencies and test commands\n7. Look for any references to \"AR-041\" or \"ST-3\" in the codebase\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- Project structure overview\n- What the application does (main purpose)\n- Existing test infrastructure and patterns\n- What components exist that would need e2e testing\n- Any existing stage/design documentation\n- Key files and their locations","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2845c2a2bffetEAiC1Je7wjpZI (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a thorough understanding of the entire project. Here is the comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive AgentCube Project Summary\n\n### 1. Project Structure Overview\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n├── .github/workflows/          # CI/CD pipelines (e2e.yml, lint.yml, test-coverage.yml, etc.)\n├── changes/                    # AR (Action Request) directories AR-001 through AR-041\n│   └── AR-XXX/                 # Each contains: proposal.md, design.md, delta-spec.md, tasks.md\n├── cmd/                        # Go binary entry points\n│   ├── agentd/main.go          # Agent daemon (controller-runtime reconciler for idle cleanup)\n│   ├── cli/                    # Python CLI toolkit (agentcube package)\n│   ├── picod/main.go           # PicoD server (code execution engine with auth)\n│   ├── router/                 # Reverse proxy router (Gin HTTP, JWT auth, session routing)\n│   └── workloadmanager/        # Workload manager API (sandbox lifecycle via Gin HTTP)\n├── pkg/                        # Go library packages\n│   ├── agentd/                 # Idle cleanup reconciler\n│   ├── apis/                   # CRD type definitions (runtime/v1alpha1, agents/)\n│   ├── common/                 # Shared types (types.SandboxInfo, etc.)\n│   ├── picod/                  # PicoD server logic (auth, execute, files, health)\n│   ├── router/                 # Router logic (proxy, JWT, loadbalancer, middleware, health)\n│   ├── store/                  # Session store (Redis, Valkey implementations)\n│   └── workloadmanager/        # Workload manager (handlers, reconciler, response, middleware)\n├── client-go/                  # Generated Kubernetes client-go library\n│   ├── clientset/              # Typed Clientset for AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter CRDs\n│   ├── informers/              # SharedInformerFactory + per-type informers\n│   └── listers/                # Lister implementations\n├── manifests/charts/base/      # Helm chart for deployment (CRDs, Deployments, Services, RBAC)\n├── test/                       # Existing test infrastructure\n│   ├── chart/test_render.sh    # Helm chart rendering tests (bash)\n│   └── makefile/test_makefile.sh # Makefile target tests (bash)\n├── testing/                    # TDD manifest\n├── docker/                     # Dockerfiles (Dockerfile, Dockerfile.router, Dockerfile.picod)\n├── deployment/                 # Deployment design docs (including design-e2e.md)\n├── integrations/dify-plugin/   # Dify platform plugin integration (Python)\n├── example/pcap_analyzer/      # Example PCAP analysis application (FastAPI + LangGraph)\n├── python-sdk/                 # Python SDK package (agentcube)\n├── session-routing/            # Session routing design/spec\n├── session-store/              # Session store design/spec\n├── code-execution/             # Code execution design/spec\n├── idle-cleanup/               # Idle cleanup design/spec\n├── cli-toolkit/                # CLI toolkit design/spec\n├── ci-cd/                      # CI/CD design/spec\n├── Makefile                    # Build system (build, test, docker, helm, python targets)\n├── go.mod                      # Go module: github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube (Go 1.25.0)\n├── design.md                   # AR-040: Python SDK/CLI unit tests design\n├── delta-spec.md               # AR-038: Go unit tests (workloadmanager) delta spec\n├── proposal.md                 # AR-036: Dify plugin integration proposal\n├── tasks.md                    # AR-023: CLI invoke/status commands tasks\n└── test_spec.md                # Test specification document\n```\n\n### 2. What the Application Does (Main Purpose)\n\n**AgentCube** is a Kubernetes-native sandbox platform for AI agent code execution. It provides:\n\n- **Sandbox Management**: Creates isolated sandboxes (pods) for code execution via two CRD types:\n  - `AgentRuntime` -- General-purpose agent runtime sandboxes\n  - `CodeInterpreter` -- Code interpreter sandboxes with warm pool support\n- **Four Core Binaries**:\n  1. **workloadmanager** -- HTTP API (Gin) for sandbox lifecycle (create/delete/query sessions), backed by Kubernetes dynamic client and a session store\n  2. **router** -- Reverse proxy (Gin) that routes HTTP requests to the correct sandbox pod, with JWT authentication and session sticky routing\n  3. **agentd** -- Controller-runtime reconciler that monitors sandbox idle timeouts and performs automatic cleanup\n  4. **picod** -- In-sandbox code execution server with JWT-based auth, file management, and command execution\n- **Session Store**: Redis/Valkey-backed session persistence for sandbox metadata, entry points, and activity tracking\n- **Python SDK/CLI**: High-level Python client (`agentcube`) for programmatic sandbox interaction, plus a CLI tool for agent management\n- **Dify Integration**: Plugin for the Dify AI platform to call AgentCube code interpreters from workflows\n- **Helm Deployment**: Full Kubernetes deployment via Helm chart with RBAC, CRDs, and optional Volcano scheduler integration\n\n### 3. Existing Test Infrastructure and Patterns\n\n#### Go Unit Tests (35+ test files)\n- **Location**: Co-located with source (`pkg/*/` directories, `*_test.go` files)\n- **Framework**: Standard `testing` package + `github.com/stretchr/testify` (assert/require)\n- **Pattern**: Table-driven tests, `t.Cleanup()` for teardown, `t.Helper()` for test helpers\n- **Key test files**:\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/router/router_test.go` -- httptest.NewRecorder/Server pattern\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/store_redis_test.go` -- miniredis for in-memory Redis testing\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/server_test.go` -- HTTP handler tests\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` -- controller reconciler tests\n  - `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` -- sandbox lifecycle\n\n#### Python Tests\n- **Location**: `python-sdk/tests/`, `cmd/cli/tests/`, `integrations/dify-plugin/tests/`, `example/pcap_analyzer/tests/`\n- **Framework**: pytest with unittest.mock\n- **Pattern**: Fixtures in `conftest.py`, MagicMock for HTTP mocking, `patch.dict(os.environ)` for env isolation\n\n#### Bash Script Tests\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test/chart/test_render.sh` -- Helm chart rendering validation\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test/makefile/test_makefile.sh` -- Makefile target verification\n\n#### Makefile Test Targets\n- `make test` -- `go test ./...`\n- `make test-coverage` -- `go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...`\n- `make test-chart` -- Helm chart render test\n- `make python-test` -- pytest for Python SDK + CLI\n- **Note**: `make e2e` and `make e2e-clean` are referenced in CI but NOT YET implemented in the Makefile\n\n#### CI/CD Workflows\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.github/workflows/e2e.yml` -- Already configured with Kind v0.30.0, calls `make e2e` (which does not exist yet)\n- Other workflows: lint, test-coverage, python-lint, python-sdk-tests, build-push-release, codespell, copyright-check, codegen-check\n\n### 4. Components That Need E2E Testing\n\n| Component | Binary | Key Endpoints/Behaviors |\n|-----------|--------|------------------------|\n| **workloadmanager** | `cmd/workloadmanager` | POST `/v1/agent-runtime`, POST `/v1/code-interpreter`, DELETE `/v1/sessions/{id}` |\n| **router** | `cmd/router` | Proxy `/invoke/agent-runtime/{ns}/{name}/*`, `/invoke/code-interpreter/{ns}/{name}/*`, health endpoints `/health/live`, `/health/ready` |\n| **agentd** | `cmd/agentd` | Idle timeout detection, sandbox cleanup via controller-runtime |\n| **picod** | `cmd/picod` | Code execution API, file upload/download, JWT validation |\n| **Session Store** | `pkg/store` | Redis/Valkey session persistence, expiry tracking, activity updates |\n| **client-go** | `client-go/` | AgentRuntime CRUD, CodeInterpreter CRUD, Informers, Listers, Watch |\n| **Helm Chart** | `manifests/charts/base/` | Full deployment, CRD installation, RBAC, Service endpoints |\n| **CRDs** | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` | AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter custom resources |\n\n### 5. Existing Stage/Design Documentation for AR-041 (E2E Tests)\n\n**AR-041: E2E Integration Tests** -- This is the current active AR being designed. Key files:\n\n| File | Location | Status |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| **Proposal** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md` | Complete -- defines scope, architecture, 19 test cases across 4 categories |\n| **Design** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/design.md` | Skeleton -- mostly TODO placeholders |\n| **Delta Spec** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/delta-spec.md` | Complete -- 15 detailed requirements (R-1 through R-15) with Given/When/Then scenarios |\n| **Tasks** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/tasks.md` | Skeleton -- T-1/T-2/T-3 are all TODO |\n| **Deployment E2E Design** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design-e2e.md` | **Most complete** -- 571 lines with full architecture, test suites, fixtures, execution flow |\n| **SDD Prompt** | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` | Contains the client-go spec reference for AR-041 |\n\n**Key design decisions already made:**\n- **Cluster**: Kind v0.30.0 (matches CI workflow)\n- **Test Framework**: Ginkgo + Gomega (proposal) vs. standard testing + testify (delta-spec) -- there is a discrepancy\n- **Deployment**: Full Helm chart deployment with all components\n- **Isolation**: Shared cluster + per-test namespace + TestMain cleanup\n- **Test Images**: nginx:1.25-alpine for sandbox pods\n- **Execution**: `make e2e` -> create Kind -> load images -> helm install -> run tests -> cleanup\n\n### 6. Key Files and Their Locations\n\n| Category | File | Absolute Path |\n|----------|------|---------------|\n| **Build** | Makefile | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile` |\n| **Go Module** | go.mod | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod` |\n| **E2E CI** | e2e.yml | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.github/workflows/e2e.yml` |\n| **AR-041 Proposal** | proposal.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md` |\n| **AR-041 Design** | design.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/design.md` |\n| **AR-041 Delta Spec** | delta-spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/delta-spec.md` |\n| **AR-041 Tasks** | tasks.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/tasks.md` |\n| **E2E Design (Detailed)** | design-e2e.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design-e2e.md` |\n| **Helm Chart** | Chart.yaml | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` |\n| **Helm Values** | values.yaml | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` |\n| **AgentRuntime CRD** | CRD YAML | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` |\n| **CodeInterpreter CRD** | CRD YAML | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` |\n| **Router main** | main.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/router/main.go` |\n| **WorkloadManager main** | main.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/workloadmanager/main.go` |\n| **AgentD main** | main.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/agentd/main.go` |\n| **PicoD main** | main.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/picod/main.go` |\n| **Sample Go Test** | router_test.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/router/router_test.go` |\n| **Sample Go Test** | store_redis_test.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/store/store_redis_test.go` |\n| **Chart Test** | test_render.sh | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test/chart/test_render.sh` |\n| **Makefile Test** | test_makefile.sh | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test/makefile/test_makefile.sh` |\n| **client-go Clientset** | clientset.go | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go` |\n\n### 7. AR-041 and ST-3 References\n\n- **AR-041** is found in 6 files: the 4 files under `changes/AR-041/`, plus `deployment/design-e2e.md` and `.sdd_prompt.md`\n- **ST-3** (Stage 3: Design Complete) is referenced in the precondition of **every** AR's tasks.md file (AR-002 through AR-041), indicating the project follows a staged development workflow where ST-3 (Design) must be completed before implementation tasks begin\n- The `test/e2e/` directory does **not exist yet** -- it is entirely planned but not created\n- The `make e2e` and `make e2e-clean` targets are **not yet implemented** in the Makefile but are already referenced by `.github/workflows/e2e.yml`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2845c2a2bffetEAiC1Je7wjpZI","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775895827921,"end":1775896067233}}}}
