TestMain(m *testing.M) {\n62:     // TODO: setup test environment\n63:     code := m.Run()\n64:     // TODO: teardown\n65:     os.Exit(code)\n66: }\n67: ```\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## 4. Coverage Targets\n72: \n73: | Sub-Module | Target Coverage | Rationale |\n74: |------------|-----------------|-----------|\n75: | test/e2e/ | TODO | TODO |\n76: \n77: ---\n78: \n79: ## 5. Implementation Notes\n80: \n81: <!-- TODO: Add implementation-specific notes -->\n\n(End of file - total 81 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-041: E2E 集成测试 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n<!-- TODO: Describe the purpose -->\n\n### 1.2 System Context\n\n```\ntest/e2e/\n├── *_test.go         # TODO — new E2E test files\n├── fixtures/         # TODO — test fixtures\n└── helpers/          # TODO — test helpers\n```\n\n### 1.3 Design Principles\n\n- **Go testing**: Use standard `testing` package with `go test`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/design.md","time":{"start":1775896074026,"end":1775896074033}}}}
